    "description": "<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索新的‘海贼王’独家活动！</h2></strong><br>让那些海贼王以黑暗领主的名义沉入海底吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118000/extras/c9161d06627a99525300198061837a78.poster.avif?t=1739448607\" width=620 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118000/extras/c9161d06627a99525300198061837a78.webm?t=1739448607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118000/extras/c9161d06627a99525300198061837a78.mp4?t=1739448607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>扬帆起航，进攻岛屿！</strong><br>击败全新的原创关卡和奇怪的头目！<br><br>5个新关卡：探索所有岛屿和巢穴，遇到烦人的新敌人。<br>为5个“海盗王”准备炮弹！<br><br>每个关卡提供3种不同模式：战役，英雄和铁。<br>掠夺海盗王的岛屿，获取他们的隐藏宝藏！<br><br>新敌人：击败海盗，海盗船长，炸弹鹦鹉，甚至顽皮的猴子！<br>当然，还有与5个国王，包括一个熟悉的面孔，进行令人兴奋的boss战…<br><br><strong>用这些强大的新角色扭转战局！</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118000/extras/8010686024cb81e5a826c749ef5be21e.poster.avif?t=1739448607\" width=620 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118000/extras/8010686024cb81e5a826c749ef5be21e.webm?t=1739448607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118000/extras/8010686024cb81e5a826c749ef5be21e.mp4?t=1739448607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>新英雄：“卢塞尔娜”，拥有幽灵般的隐形能力和强大火力的邪鬼队长。<br><br>新塔：食人魔沉船，一艘被战争贩子用作行动基地的废弃船只。<br><br><strong>而且，像往常一样...</strong><br><br>众多新成就：没有美味宝藏的海盗冒险还算什么？<br><br>很多复活节彩蛋：永远不会太深，笑话也可以浮出水面 <br><br>将军，将他们的旗帜带到维兹南！<br>向这些不听话的海盗释放你的愤怒，以纪念他的黑暗统治。<br><i>黑暗军团指望你来完成这个新任务</i>",
